@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Flight Control Operator" as FCO
participant ":System" as System
participant ":Report Generation Thread" as ReportThread
participant ":Shared Memory" as SharedMemory
participant ":Simulation Report" as Report

activate FCO

FCO -> System : Requests simulation report

activate System
System --> System : Check if FCO is authenticated and authorized
System --> System : Validate selected simulation
System -> ReportThread : Request report generation

activate ReportThread
ReportThread -> SharedMemory : Read simulation configuration
activate SharedMemory
SharedMemory --> ReportThread : Simulation configuration
deactivate SharedMemory

ReportThread -> SharedMemory : Read included flights and process statuses
activate SharedMemory
SharedMemory --> ReportThread : Flights and process statuses
deactivate SharedMemory

ReportThread -> SharedMemory : Read aircraft position history
activate SharedMemory
SharedMemory --> ReportThread : Position history
deactivate SharedMemory

ReportThread -> SharedMemory : Read safety violation events
activate SharedMemory
SharedMemory --> ReportThread : Safety violation events
deactivate SharedMemory

ReportThread -> Report : Compile simulation report
activate Report
Report --> ReportThread : Report compiled
deactivate Report

ReportThread --> System : Simulation report
deactivate ReportThread

alt report generated successfully
    System --> FCO : Display simulation report
else report generation fails
    System --> FCO : Display report generation error
end

deactivate System
deactivate FCO

@enduml